text:
Ofício remetido pelo TFM de Faro relativo à decisão judicial no Apenso A do Proc.
[redacted_id], datado de 09.08.2024, de fls. 766 a 767;
Ofício do TFM contendo cópia da Acta de Conferência de Pais no Apenso A do
Proc. [redacted_id], de fls. 785 a 787;
Cópias de mensagens, de fls. 798; e respectiva tradução, de fls. 799v;
Ofício da CPCJ de Loulé referente aos filhos menores do casal, informando que os
mesmos estão a ser acompanhados pelo TFM de Faro, de fls. 832;
Pen Drive contendo os vídeos e fotografias das lesões e maus tratos aos menores
na contracapa do Vol. III.
Auto de inquirição, gravado com som e imagem, da ofendida perante Magistrado do Ministério Público(diligênciaqueocorreue m05.09.2024),
requerendo-se a sua reprodução no interrogatório, caso s e considere indispensável para reforço da prova;

trans:
Official communication from the Faro Family and Minors Court (TFM) regarding the judicial decision in Appendix A of Case No.
[redacted_id], dated August 9, 2024, pages 766 to 767;
Official communication from the TFM containing a copy of the Parent Conference Record in Appendix A of
Case No. [redacted_id], pages 785 to 787;
Copies of messages, page 798; and their respective translations on page 799v;
Official communication from the Loulé Child and Youth Protection Commission (CPCJ) concerning the minor children of the couple, indicating that
they are being monitored by the Faro Family and Minors Court (TFM), page 832;
A flash drive containing videos and photographs of the injuries and mistreatment of the minors
located on the back cover of Volume III.
Recorded testimony of the victim, with audio and video, presented before a Public Prosecutor Magistrate (during a hearing on September 5, 2024),
with a request for its playback during interrogation if deemed essential to reinforce the evidence;
